query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 t1 tq1 u1 s) NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 1
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('async-await',
'beautifulsoup',
'canvas',
'colors',
'doctrine-orm',
'eloquent',
'html',
'linked-list',
'nhibernate',
'permissions',
'postgis',
'redis',
'spring-boot',
'visual-studio-2010')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('english',
'es',
'gis',
'stackoverflow',
'unix')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Explainer',
'Good Question') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
